Project 1: CORE HR Infrastructure (Banking Sector)

Worked on developing and maintaining an HR Module application used in the banking sector to manage large-scale employee transactions. 
The system was built using ASP.NET MVC, .NET Core, C#, Entity Framework Core, Hangfire, and SQL Server.
The application handled employee data processing, automated background jobs, and ensured reliable and secure HR operations.

Project 2: Production Support & Error Monitoring System

Worked on monitoring and resolving production issues to ensure high system availability and performance. 
The application was built using ASP.NET MVC, C#, Entity Framework, SQL Server, and Serilog for logging. 
Responsibilities included analyzing errors, identifying root causes, fixing bugs, and improving system stability.
